{"tid":1955880,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係父母面前自殺係咪對佢地最好既懲罰？","createTime":"2020-04-02T19:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T13:32:59.000Z","uid":201604,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"27c1f484a4122adfa80308b9b375070443a84a88","tid":1955880,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T19:23:46.000Z","msg":"純討論 我唔夠膽 夠膽一早去死解脫左仲邊得閒理佢地"},{"pid":"f719363d9b1bec42724cb3d984f21a8acc1d6552","tid":1955880,"uid":343964,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T19:33:14.000Z","msg":"窮撚生仔女正仆街 仲要生得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c832f8a50d8708b6b966c7e13f4e966b08617f75","tid":1955880,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:05:11.000Z","msg":"搞咩"},{"pid":"4d1e28694b06bd12673fe8ca7dc0b1dbe5b94898","tid":1955880,"uid":113830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:14:44.000Z","msg":"係 割喉"},{"pid":"fa4120bf26f0a10bce6a5c54d3c9c7cf3b0ca011","tid":1955880,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T21:18:15.000Z","msg":"唔好呀毒毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9aabf6c08573eecfb5294e1cbebb7b6c750521e","tid":1955880,"uid":154255,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T22:11:39.000Z","msg":"愛你嘅難受<br />\n唔愛你嘅無感<br />\n做嚟有乜謂"},{"pid":"88340223c255168032ef5333f4de38c4233c35ee","tid":1955880,"uid":122513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27c1f484a4122adfa80308b9b375070443a84a88","tid":1955880,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T19:23:46.000Z","msg":"純討論 我唔夠膽 夠膽一早去死解脫左仲邊得閒理佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，到我們的網站   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=4f6687f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=0335c246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a> ）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"6e71f6c61f160f4239a55f233786ab21d85c307d","tid":1955880,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"99d5fdf22a2841cb8fb976926f7bc82db5ec9053","tid":1955880,"uid":24615,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"佢地會消費你 <br />\n同出面人講死左個仔好慘點點點<br />\n以受害者自居 <br />\n<br />\n好似佢仲慘過你咁<br />\n然後d人暗暗地指責你唔孝順<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後如果你有人壽就比佢地貪埋"},{"pid":"85df1cdb44e7f47ea77cbc2c9b167335bcfefc73","tid":1955880,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:11:06.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"414b92119ef175c2fe7d99eeeefd410b28f75fb8","tid":1955880,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"係送佢去老人院呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6d3e45889e8d9a94c67998b4e1189c6e399af4","tid":1955880,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"414b92119ef175c2fe7d99eeeefd410b28f75fb8","tid":1955880,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"係送佢去老人院呀<img sr